{"text_id":19007,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," cosmic","-","ray"," (","CR",")"," pressure"," in"," galaxy"," clusters"," using"," observations"," of"," gamma","-","ray"," emission"," from"," the"," decay"," of"," relativistic"," electrons",".","  ","Gamma","-","ray"," telescopes",","," sensitive"," to"," electron"," energies"," above"," ","1"," GeV",","," provide"," a"," unique"," tool"," for"," probing"," the"," CR"," pressure","."," Extremely"," energetic"," CR","s",","," often"," associated"," with"," active"," galactic"," nuclei"," and"," supernova"," remnants",","," may"," contribute"," significantly"," to"," the"," overall"," pressure"," in"," galaxy"," clusters","."," The"," high"," energy"," of"," these"," CR","s"," allows"," for"," an"," indirect"," estimation"," of"," their"," pressure"," through"," inverse"," Compton"," scattering"," off"," the"," cosmic"," microwave"," background"," and"," intra","cluster"," medium"," photons",","," manifesting"," as"," gamma","-","ray"," emission",".","  ","We"," employ"," a"," multi","-","wavelength"," approach",","," combining"," gamma","-","ray"," observations"," from"," Fermi","-","LAT"," with"," X","-","ray"," and"," optical"," data","."," We"," model"," the"," observed"," gamma","-","ray","  ","spectra",","," accounting"," for"," different"," CR"," injection"," scenarios"," and"," propagation"," mechanisms"," within"," the"," cluster"," environment","."," Our"," aim"," is"," to"," constrain"," the"," CR"," pressure"," profile",","," shedding"," light"," on"," the"," dynamics"," and"," evolution"," of"," galaxy"," clusters","."," Furthermore",","," we"," explore"," the"," cosmological"," implications"," of"," our"," findings",","," investigating"," the"," role"," of"," CR","s"," in"," the"," large","-","scale"," structure"," formation"," and"," cosmic"," energy"," budget","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma2-9b-it","label":1}